Alpha Course: Are You New Here?||<h3>"Is there more to life?"<br />"What am I doing here?"<br />"Is this it?"</h3>
<p><strong>Do you ever find yourself asking questions like these?</strong>&nbsp;If so...come join us for the next Alpha Course. Whether you are new to the faith or if you have been a Christian for awhile, this is welcoming place for you to come and explore the meaning of life and faith with other people on the same journey of discovery.</p>
<h3>Who is Alpha for?</h3>
<p>Alpha is open to all people of all ages and backgrounds.&nbsp; If you are open-minded and interested in engaging in conversations regarding your faith then this is a great spot for you.&nbsp; We will look at the basics of the Christian faith and talk about how that relates to our every day lives.</p>
<h3>What Can I Expect?</h3>
<p>The format is a short message and discussion. Childcare is provided. There is no charge for the Alpha course &ndash; donations for materials are accepted.</p>
